data.name: Info2.Text
data.value: Contact tracing helps stop the spread of infectious diseases by breaking chains of transmission. Fraser Health contact tracers work to support COVID-19 patients and notify their contacts of exposure to the virus.

data.name: Info4.Text
data.value: Get tested as soon as you start to feel even a little bit sick. The sooner we know about a positive case, the sooner we can start contact tracing. If you test positive, complete the COVID-19 Case and Contact Form right away to help speed up the contact tracing process.
